STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
Nathaniel HARVEY, Defendant-Respondent. M-1079 September Term 2017
080098 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 4, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for relaxation of the Court Rules on copy requirements is dismissed as moot, the Court having received electronic copies of the transcripts from the Appellate Division.
